{"word":"G677 - ἀπρόσκοπος - apróskopos - ap-ros'-kop-os - None","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπρόσκοπος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apróskopos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ros'-kop-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">None</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குற்றமற்ற, இடறலற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"having nothing for one to strike against; not causing to stumble"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G4350 - προσκόπτω - proskóptō - pros-kop'-to/4350\">G4350</a>; actively <i>inoffensive</i>, that is, <i>not leading into sin</i>; passively <i>faultless</i>, that is, <i>not led into sin:</i> - none (void of, without) offence.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4348/4348\">G4348</a>, <a href=\"#/G4349/4349\">G4349</a>, <a href=\"#/G4350/4350\">G4350</a>, <a href=\"#/G677/677\">G677</a>"}]}